      "value": "<strong>Bloodrager - Bloodline</strong><br/><br/><p>The Pit lives in your blood. Maybe one of your ancestors was seduced by the powers of Hell or made a deal with a devil. Either way, its corruption seethes within your lineage.</p><p><b>Bonus Feats: </b>Blind-Fight, Combat Reflexes, Deceitful, Improved Disarm, Improved Sunder, Intimidating Prowess, Iron Will.</p><p><b>Bonus Spells: </b>protection from good (7th), scorching ray (10th), suggestion (13th), fire shield (16th)</p><p><b>Bloodline Powers: </b>When you bloodrage, hellfire infuses your blood with terrifying effects.</p>",
